      "title": "President Putin congratulates Ranil W on election to office of President",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st): Russian President Vladimir Putin has congratulated President \u00a0Ranil Wickremesinghe\u2019s election to the office of the Presidency.",
        "In a letter addressed to President Wickremesinghe, the Russian President had also expressed his hopes to further strengthen relations between the two nations.",
        "\u201cI am counting on your activities as Head of State to foster further development of the constructive bilateral cooperation in various spheres for the benefits of our peoples and in the interest of strengthening the regional stability and security,\u201d Russian President Vladimir Putin further said in the letter",
        "Travel ban against six activists including Rev. Fr. Jeewantha, & IUSF Chief",
        "President Putin congratulates Ranil W on election to office of President",
        "Fuel Pass: Implementation from 26th July; Only QR based service from 1st August",
        "Three men nabbed while trying to sell loot from President\u2019s Office"
      ],
